---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="About" description="About this AI art portfolio.">
  <h1 class="page-title">About</h1>
  <div class="prose">
    <p>
      This site showcases AI-generated and digital art. Replace this paragraph with your own story:
      how you got into generative art, which tools you use, and what you’re exploring.
    </p>
    <p>
      You can add more sections, links to socials, or a short bio. Edit this file at
      <code>src/pages/about.astro</code>.
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>
